## ğŸ” Data Safety & GitHub Usage

- Sample data uses dummy emails, phone numbers, and passwords
- No real user credentials are stored
- Safe to upload for GitHub portfolio and demo purposes

---

## ğŸ¯ Why This Database Design

- Mirrors real-world online food delivery platforms
- Clean separation of users, restaurants, menus, and orders
- Supports transactional consistency
- Easy to explain in interviews and system design discussions
- Ready for future upgrades (Spring Boot, JPA, REST APIs)
